OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStorm Dave
OL,6,Fwill bring strong winds and coastal
OL,7,Fgales this evening, particularly
OL,8,Faround exposed coasts of north and
OL,9,Fnorthwest Wales. Heavy and blustery
OL,10,Fspells of rain to start then the storm
OL,11,Fwill clear in the early hours as winds
OL,12,Fease.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FSunny spells and scattered
OL,15,Fshowers on Easter Day with lighter
OL,16,Fwinds. Mostly dry by the afternoon but
OL,17,Ffeeling colder than previous days with
OL,18,Fa fresh breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
